 *          9 character per pair of 36 bit words.
 *
 *    36b   Bit numbers using              bit
 *   word   standard bit numbering   byte  offset
 *      0 - 35 34 33 32 31 30 29 28     0     0
 *      0 - 27 26 25 24 23 22 21 20     1     8
 *      0 - 19 18 17 16 15 14 13 12     2    16
